steps

* install Ubuntu
* append this to /etc/sudoers:
    kevan ALL ALL=(ALL) NOPASSWD: ALL
* apt install sway
* download & install chrome
    * download & install 1password
    * log into 1password in chrome
    * load blank new tab page extension
* uninstall snap

* apt install git alacritty tmux neovim
* set up ssh keys
* clone this repo
* run update_configs
* log out and back in

* install keyd, copy configs, reload
* apt install ripgrep git-delta fd-find

* change grub timeout to 2 seconds
* if you're dual-booting windows:
    timedatectl set-local-rtc 1
